Subject: Re: [T2] Another broken-off easy-out

Try going at the bolt with a small chisel.  Once the bolt breaks there 
is often very little force locking the threads in place. Sometimes a 
good smack with a hammer via a brass punch is all that is needed to get 
it to unscrew.

Jim


